3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses a scheduling algorithm for controlling the order of work to be performed by a computer system, which falls under this sub-category.
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): Cloud computing heavily relies on networking and internet architecture, and the paper discusses scheduling in this context.
